description:
Brennan is actually friends with one of our most popular models and was sent to us by him.

“He said it was a good time and that I would be a good fit, so I figured why the hell not?”
“Do you think that maybe you would do more than a solo?” I had to ask.
“Let’s take it one day at time here.” He started to laugh.

Brennan is a great guy with an even greater body. He just recently got into body building shows and has loved all of the attention.

“I get a lot of compliments on my abs. It really helps with the ego, you know.” 

As it should, Brennan has some of the tightest abs we have seen around here.
title: Brennan
